{"tid":2419314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次區議會宣誓係俾區議員出走海外組流亡議會嘅一大契機","createTime":"2021-02-23T08:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T09:04:02.000Z","uid":309558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"89175622356da45840260450b471e58405ae5a67","tid":2419314,"uid":309558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"好明顯地港共政權已經準備想清洗咁多個區議員，你見就算泛民喺立法會跪住咁入議會都一樣俾人Dq,更甚至要追收佢哋嗰幾個月嘅糧<br />\n<br />\n所以宣唔宣誓其實唔係重點，因為佢點都會搞鳩成個民主派嘅區議員，更甚者可能會再次有大搜捕出現<br />\n<br />\n而家可以走到嘅就應該立即要走，香港需要有真正代表香港人嘅議會，現時香港有300名以上嘅民主派區議員，亦加上區議員係真正地得到民意授權，相信組流亡議會進行國際遊說工作係最有作用"},{"pid":"aff361e4d7d2dd2ab536abfd748fbd615c34b56b","tid":2419314,"uid":309558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e4ec2b9527b2a0a075917a47da256e8cc82a00","tid":2419314,"uid":309558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72629e18360e98a71c0c70e1874f07bbd545c7cb","tid":2419314,"uid":309558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:48:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4b9e36780fc006038dd1d6d24e1cf50a0f5967","tid":2419314,"uid":309558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c7615804c676a508a0af0fb95d1e6c8b2dce15","tid":2419314,"uid":309558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:52:54.000Z","msg":"如果真係決定要宣誓留低，咁係咪有把握宣誓完佢就唔會dq你?<br />\n<br />\n同埋係咪有把握自己日後唔會俾國安法拘捕而冇得出走海外?"},{"pid":"e77eab3f6321dc399d36e6ed95617daeb2b0ee03","tid":2419314,"uid":309558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"